href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Work-Pictures/Misc-1-Cessna/i-nc7hvvh\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Work-Pictures/Misc-1-Cessna/i-nc7hvvh/0/L/Image07-L.jpg\"></a><br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),(7,'2015-02-03','Test Entry','\r\ntest\r\n'),(14,'2017-10-10','How to configure Kodi for Android TV','\r\n<p>\r\nI prefer SPMC to Kodi. It is a fork of Kodi that is coded for Android operating systems and runs much faster.</p><p>You can get it on the google play store or download the apk here.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://spmc.semperpax.com/\">http://spmc.semperpax.com/</a></p><p>I prefer a vertical menu that can be adjusted to my liking. The MIMIC theme is available from the Kodi repository. Just go to the settings/appearance and click on skin. Then get more. Then choose MIMIC.</p><p><br></p>\r\n'),(16,'2017-10-10','Another Post','Another test post.'),(17,'2018-10-25','Device Manager during Windows 7 setup','<br style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: verdana, geneva, lucida, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13.3333px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(246,=\"\" 250,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: verdana, geneva, lucida, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13.3333px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(246,=\"\" 250,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\"><u><font size=\"6\"><font color=\"green\">Here\'s How:</font></font></u></strong><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: verdana, geneva, lucida, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13.3333px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(246,=\"\" 250,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\"><br><div align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#000000\">1,&nbsp;<font size=\"2\">B<font color=\"black\">oot normally with the Windows 7 DVD in your CD/DVD drive. When prompted to \'Press any key to boot from CD DVD....\' just press any key.</font></font></font></font></div><br><br><br><div align=\"left\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong><font color=\"red\">NOTE:</font></strong>&nbsp;<em>You only have 8 seconds to take action</em></font></div><br><br><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#000000\">2,&nbsp;<font size=\"2\">Select your regional settings &amp; click \'Next\' to continue</font></font></font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17222d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-1-main-menu-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17222\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17222d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-1-main-menu-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-1-main-menu-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-1-main-menu-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">3,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Click \'Install Now\'</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17223d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-2-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17223\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17223d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-2-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-2-install-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-2-install-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">4,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Click to accept the terms of the licence agreement then click \'Next\'</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17224d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-3-licence-agreement-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17224\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17224d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-3-licence-agreement-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-3-licence-agreement-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-3-licence-agreement-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"black\">5,&nbsp;<font size=\"2\"><font color=\"black\">Select the type of install and click \'Next\'</font></font></font></font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17225d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-4-custom-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17225\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17225d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-4-custom-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-4-custom-install-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-4-custom-install-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">6,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"black\">Click \'Drive options\'</font></font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17226d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-5-drive-options-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17226\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17226d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-5-drive-options-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-5-drive-options-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-5-drive-options-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">7,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Click \'New\'</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17227d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-6-new-partition-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17227\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17227d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-6-new-partition-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6-new-partition-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6-new-partition-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><blockquote>and enter partition size then click \'Apply\'<br><br><br><br><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17228d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-6.1-new-partition-size-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6.1-new-partition-size-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6.1-new-partition-size-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></div><br><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">8,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Click \'Next\' to start the copying process of the installation</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17229d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-7-next-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17229\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17229d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-7-next-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-7-next-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-7-next-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br><br></blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17230d1247139498-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-8-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17230\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17230d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-8-install-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-8-install-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-8-install-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">9,</font>&nbsp;Install will restart after the copying process has finished.<br><br><br><br></blockquote><strong style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: verdana, geneva, lucida, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13.3333px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(246,=\"\" 250,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\"><font size=\"6\"><font color=\"green\"><u>Now for Safe Mode:</u></font></font></strong><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: verdana, geneva, lucida, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13.3333px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(246,=\"\" 250,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\"><div align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"black\">1,&nbsp;<font size=\"2\">Before bootup, press F8 to enter the boot menu</font></font></font></div><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17232d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-1a-safe-mode-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17232\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17232d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-1a-safe-mode-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-1a-safe-mode-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-1a-safe-mode-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">2,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Select \'Safe Mode\' and the boot process will begin</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17233d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-2a-safe-mode-booting-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17233\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17233d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-2a-safe-mode-booting-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-2a-safe-mode-booting-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-2a-safe-mode-booting-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">3,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Once booted you will be presented with the following warning</font><br><strong><font color=\"red\">NOTE:</font></strong>&nbsp;<em>Do not click \'OK\' or press Space/Enter</em><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17234d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-3a-safe-mode-warning-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17234\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17234d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-3a-safe-mode-warning-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-3a-safe-mode-warning-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-3a-safe-mode-warning-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">4,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Press SHIFT+F10 to open the Command Prompt</font><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17235d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-4a-safe-mode-command-prompt-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17235\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17235d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-4a-safe-mode-command-prompt-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-4a-safe-mode-command-prompt-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-4a-safe-mode-command-prompt-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">5,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Type&nbsp;<strong>compmgmtlauncher&nbsp;</strong>into Command Prompt and press \'Enter\'</font><br><font color=\"red\"><strong>NOTE:</strong></font>&nbsp;<em>It can take a few seconds to display Computer Management</em><blockquote><br><div align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17236d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-5a-safe-mode-computer-management-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17236\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 133, 189); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17236d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-5a-safe-mode-computer-management-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-5a-safe-mode-computer-management-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-5a-safe-mode-computer-management-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a></div><br><br><br></blockquote><font size=\"4\">6,&nbsp;</font><font size=\"2\">Click on \'Device Manager\'</font><blockquote><br><div align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17237d1247140139-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-6a-safe-mode-device-manager-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" rel=\"Lightbox_161885\" id=\"attachment17237\" style=\"color: rgb(98, 175, 167); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://www.sevenforums.com/attachments/tutorials/17237d1486565019t-device-manager-access-during-windows-7-installation-install-7-step-6a-safe-mode-device-manager-.png?s=c40c20ace08c101a02765755d5554620\" class=\"thumbnail\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6a-safe-mode-device-manager-.png\" title=\"Device Manager - Access During Windows 7 Installation-install-7-step-6a-safe-mode-device-manager-.png\" style=\"margin: 2px;\"></a></div><br><br><br><br><br><br></blockquote>You can now disable (not uninstall) any device that you believe is causing the failure to boot</blockquote>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n');
