2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-3p8GmPg\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-3p8GmPg/0/L/IMG_0895-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-8BvXC6K\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-8BvXC6K/0/L/IMG_0899-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-jnWW9Ks\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-jnWW9Ks/0/L/IMG_0900-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-zqMJTVF\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-zqMJTVF/0/L/casino_bar_all_of_us-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-qnLbrmS\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-qnLbrmS/0/L/IMG_0912-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-fDhKKDX\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-fDhKKDX/0/L/IMG_0922-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-gjSnLDX\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-gjSnLDX/0/L/IMG_0926-L.jpg\"></a><br><a style=\"display:block;padding-bottom:10px;\" href=\"https://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Funny-Pictures/Funny-Pictures1/i-kRThSR4\" alt=\"Smugmug link\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"750\" class=\"sel_image\" src=\"https://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Funny-Pictures/Funny-Pictures1/i-kRThSR4/0/621319e5/L/giantsaw-L.jpg\"></a><br><br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),(8,'2014-10-13','Triumph','\r\n<font size=\"5\">\r\nWe joined our friend Brent and his family for their first cruise. We departed Galveston for Progreso, Mexico and Cozumel Mexico on a 5 day cruise.\r\n\r\nIt was a blast. We had a great time. October is a great time to cruise.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe\'ve heard so much about Buc-ees, so this time we actually went there. It is a huge place just north of Houston. They have lots of jerky, snacks, sandwiches and lots of gas pumps. Pretty cool.\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-KqpH9M8\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-KqpH9M8/0/XL/IMG_0822-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-FXNVgD3\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-FXNVgD3/0/XL/IMG_0821-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-bHJDS4b\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-bHJDS4b/0/XL/IMG_0820-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\nLots of fuzzy flasks. Who knew that was a thing in Texas?\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-J9tw2Dk\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-J9tw2Dk/0/XL/IMG_0819-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-vpGkhK2\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-vpGkhK2/0/XL/IMG_0817-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\nLook at all the jerky. Every kind you could imagine. I bought some and it was great. The smallest amount you could buy was a quarter pound.\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-RFnCGC3\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-RFnCGC3/0/XL/IMG_0818-XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\"></font></a></div><font size=\"5\">\r\nThey had two of these gas pump areas.\r\n</font><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><a href=\"http://claytonfelt.smugmug.com/Cruises/Carnival-Triumph-2014/Carnival-Triumph-2014-g/i-3qvnzHG\" target=\"_blank\"><font size=\"5\"><img src=\"htt